OOC: Speak for yourself... i ate everything in sight...  I think it has to do 
with no one telling me i was allowed to dislike things... or maybe they just 
hit me until i liked it... hard to say really.

::Aerotaur::
       He finally stands up and walks over to a computer and downloads a map 
of the base.  With that handy he walks to the quarantine bays to see his 
friend.  Upon his arrival he wanders around until he finds the observation 
window and intercom.  "Hey Windlord, I see they've got you baby-sitting.  
Who've you got there?"

--part1_19d.11ab970e.2b9405f5_boundary
